The paper focuses on the security of electronic payment systems, which is a topic that falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). Additionally, the paper discusses various cryptographic techniques and protocols used in electronic payment systems, which could also fall under the categories of cryptography (cs.CY) and information theory (cs.IT).
